{"tid":2393123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸軍方與「中共」代表會面後，便發動政變","createTime":"2021-02-03T08:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T12:13:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":162,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"1361688476709ef6fbe76574f80e8389c041bf87","tid":2393123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-03/532397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-02-03%2F532397&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=c60303a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-03/532397</a><br />\n<br />\n中國煽動緬甸政變?王毅1月訪緬見｢親中軍頭｣德執政黨發言人籲徹查<br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 楊清緣 綜合報導<br />\n發布 2021.02.03 | 04:13<br />\n。。<br />\n《德國之聲》（DW）2日報導，德國執政聯盟「基督教民主聯盟（CDU）／基督教社會聯盟（CSU）」的國會外交政策發言人哈特（Jurgen Hardt）表示，中國外交部長王毅1月才出訪緬甸，並會見與中國政府關係友好的緬甸武裝部隊總司令敏昂萊（Min Aung Hlaing），如今緬甸就發生政變，他說：「或許中方當時曾鼓勵緬軍接管國家，或者緬軍因為中國外長到訪而受到鼓舞。」並呼籲，歐盟應詳細調查整起政變的背後因素，若能掌握中國或其他外國勢力是緬甸政變幕後黑手的證據，就應該在聯合國安全理事會公開討論。"},{"pid":"01767d5d31872fd986114d96141df355af1a43db","tid":2393123,"uid":60434,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"China no.1"},{"pid":"9f783c98dbccfb1bafbf40840da7acfbcf2aeec2","tid":2393123,"uid":134071,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"安理會在中國阻隢下 未能通過譴責緬甸政變聲明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2392958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2392958</a>"},{"pid":"ff8033a9e19a29b2d0950f861893bd663d4f9f81","tid":2393123,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01767d5d31872fd986114d96141df355af1a43db","tid":2393123,"uid":60434,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"China no.1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bangh