查整起政變的背後因素，若能掌握中國或其他外國勢力是緬甸政變幕後黑手的證據，就應該在聯合國安全理事會公開討論。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7feada8652b92c67c512f5ae08370d8de19624c6","tid":2393123,"uid":90499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed13ed7aa674f66db0fd8e3e70bd2f68c7c05b1","tid":2393123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d57eeea5822837126e8296fcdf61bccf2087603","tid":2393123,"uid":365620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"美國咁都仲唔做嘢....<br />\n啊sorry，唔記得咗依家China Joe揸旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"如果係侵侵已經整左肉醬意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e978b0158de95a73f8b923c5680f58fc174ccf1","tid":2393123,"uid":93588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"中國為今次世界大戰組緊隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"9f783c98dbccfb1bafbf40840da7acfbcf2aeec2","tid":2393123,"uid":134071,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"安理會在中國阻隢下 未能通過譴責緬甸政變聲明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2392958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2392958</a>"}}